The maple/rosewood 24 fret reverse headstock neck has zero fret wear ,and Jackson logo diecast tuners.There is a small black mark on the heel of the neck near the neck plate. The cool Gloss Black body has light surface scratches. Guitar features string through the body tunematic style bridge. Hot Black/White Zebra Humbuckers . All electronics work perfectly,and sound great on every setting,clean or with some distortion. No joke these pickups sound killer on this guitar. The capacitor has been upgraded with a Orange Drop Style .022uf capacitor,more range of tone control and a smoother response. This "Custom Shack" came out great!!!
